                Users who don't login to their own Spotify account will have to all share one single Spotify account to
                make API calls. <br>
                In this case your session is starting to get rate limited because too many people are making requests.
                <br>
                Either wait a minute and try again, or login to your Spotify account to get more API calls.<br>
